            "type": "dialogue",
            "character": "shiori_nagayama",
            "portrait": "casual.smile",
            "text_ja": "うん。じゃあ、また。",
            "text_en": "Sure. See you around."
        },
        {
            "scene_id": "scene_009",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "character": "player",
            "text_ja": "（友達、って感じになったな。それはそれで、悪くない。）",
            "text_en": "(...It feels like we've settled into a friendship. That's not so bad.)"
